  "Description": {
    "English": "A personal rocketry device with a direct link to the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Galactic Trade Network</span>. This unit allows the user to load a small spacecraft with goods. Upon launch, the goods will be transported to the nearest trade terminus and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">automatically sold</span>.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Summon</span> the Trade Rocket using the <span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "直接连接至<span class=\"name name-technology\">银河交易网络</span>的私人火箭装置。这种单元将允许使用者在一艘小型太空飞船中装载货物。发射之后，飞船装载的货物将被运输至最近的贸易枢纽并<span class=\"name name-stellar\">自动出售</span>。<br><br>用<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">召唤</span>交易火箭。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "直接連結到<span class=\"name name-technology\">銀河交易網</span>的個人火箭裝置。使用者可用此裝置將商品裝入小型太空船。在發射時，商品會被運輸到最近的交易終站，並<span class=\"name name-stellar\">自動售出</span>。<br><br>使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span> 即可<span class=\"name name-stellar\">召喚</span>貿易火箭。"
  },
